   },
   "source": [
    "Let's talk about working with the data."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "collapsed": false
   },
   "source": [
    "A data Series of floating point values."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
